        been retained.
4.  Oracle Aggregate Enhancement
    -   The aggregate expressions have been updated to use Oracle’s KEEP
        (DENSE_RANK FIRST/LAST ORDER BY …) where applicable for
        first/last values, in line with Oracle best practices.

Overall, the objective of these changes was to reduce duplicate code,
improve readability and maintainability, and preserve the existing
report output and business logic.

